<p class="magenta">Welcome to the</p><p class="magenta">domain management system</p><p class="magenta">of Telekom Deutschland GmbH</p><p>The system for the registration</p><p>and management of</p><p>internet domain names</p><p>and DNS zones.</p></div><div class="modul grid_2 info modul_noH"><h3> </h3><div class="modul_ru"><div class="modul_lu"><div class="modul_inhalt " role="" aria-live="" aria-relevant="" id="" aria-atomic="" aria-busy="">
<p>If you have any questions or issues, please contact our team of experts on  <b>0800 33 01180.</b></p><p>You can reach the team from Monday - Friday from 08:00 to 20:00 and on Saturday from 08:00 to 16:00.</p><p>Or you can send us an email to the address<br /><a rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" href="mailto:dk-it@telekom.de">dk-it@telekom.de</a><br />
You will receive feedback within one business day.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="clear"></div><div id="footerContentBox:idFooterContentDiv" class="footerContent" role="contentinfo"><form id="footerContentBox:idFooterForm" name="footerContentBox:idFooterForm" method="post" action="/david/faces/pages/login/start.xhtml" enctype="application/x-www-form-urlencoded"><a href="https://www.telekom.de/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" title="Telekom">
